         <center><h3>System Background</h3></center>

                <p style="text-align: justify">
                    Alumni registration system aims to communicate with the graduated students from the ICTRC and to share the information of how they are 
                    successfully walking on their own career path. This is a web-based application system that allows to make interaction between the former 
                    students and the institutes. In addition, as students are alumni for life, it is a best way to have a long-term relationship and to keep 
                    in touch not only with each other but also with the institute. Concurrently, it will help the institutes to keep tracking the future endeavors 
                    of them for the sake of enhancing in each career path.  
                </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify">
                     In order to facilitate engagement, an alumnus who has joined as a student at the ICTRC before need to be registered with each specific roll 
                    number in this system. After accomplishing as an official member, the system will offer full acknowledgement for filling alumni survey form, 
                    for inquiring other information and for analyzing the employment report with regard to the position and sector. Each registered alumnus will 
                    be responsible for updating their own information in accordance with the latest working job details to support the faculty credits.
                </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify">
                    In today’s modernized world, as building community and wide networking becomes important to a certain extent, we wish to help all of our 
                    alumni for better communication by means of our alumni registration system.
                </p>
                
